SOLUTION(EV3(<<'END_SOLUTION'));
$BR$BBOLD Solution:$EBOLD $PAR
\( \frac{d}{dx}x^4 = 4 x^3\) , so \( \frac{d}{dx}x^4|_{x=$a}= 4($a)^3 = $derivf\).
END_SOLUTION

